nodes.text: White Squadron was a New Jedi Order squadron active in 44 ABY. It contained at least one unknown shuttle, which was unsuited for combat purposes.

White Squadron participated in a battle on Nam Chorios in a supporting role. Taryn Zel wished to rescue Jedi Knight Raynar Thul after he was shot down by a Golan III Space Defense NovaGun. She was told by Jedi Master Kyle Katarn that her shuttle was unsuitable for combat retrieval.
